 nt experience is required. This is a capstone program for rising leaders\,
  not an intro course. FUNDING: travel\, accommodation\, and meals are full
 y covered. DATES: 8-25 September 2026 at the Hopkins Bloomberg Center in W
 ashington\, D.C. (in-person only). DEADLINE: apply by 15 July 2026 for ful
