 chool of Government and Policy (SOGP)\nLocation: Hopkins Bloomberg Center\
 , Washington\, D.C. (in-person only)\nAward: Fully funded: travel\, accomm
 odation\, and meals covered.\nDuration: Three-week in-person intensive\, 8
 -25 September 2026\n\nMore: https://sogp.jh.edu/agi-governance-fellowship/
